    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, I promise you're going to love it!",
