    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2005 BMW M3 Coupe, finished in pristine Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. Every mechanical vulnerability has been proactively addressed: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced with a bespoke plate kit. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise throws, feeding power through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains incredibly taut, retaining its original geometry and bushings for a pure, analog driving experience. With zero paint correction needed and a comprehensive service dossier, this is a turn-key specimen for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Flawless interior and exterior. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
